title.narrative: Influence markets and increase access to fit-for-purpose products for children

description.narrative: This strategy aims to influence global and local markets to meet the current and future needs of children, focusing on the availability, affordability, quality and appropriateness of products, as well as the long-term competitiveness and sustainability of the markets themselves. Accelerating R&D and scale-up of future products, it also defines supplier/industry engagement strategies with the business sector.For 2021, 75% of the Supply Outcome Targets designed to provide and increase access to affordable, fit-for-purpose products and services are on track, meeting the target of 75%.From 2018 to 2021, the indicator remained on track, continuously meeting the 75% target. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:30/03/2022
